    "These networks are typified by their intricate feedforward architecture [13], often referred to as the backpropagation (BP) structure.",
    "In the domain of deep learning, CNNs have emerged as a widely utilized methodology [14][15], primarily recognized for their adeptness in the extraction of both image and abstract features.",
