    "C. Theoretical Framework of Object DetectionAlgorithms Object detection, alternatively known as object extraction, entails the recognition, correct categorization, and exact placement of objects within a given image.",
    "Yan et al. [17] unveil an unsupervised deep learning approach that adeptly separates content from noise in MRI images without the need for paired training data, a notable advancement given the complexities of diagnosing conditions like novel coronavirus pneumonia."
